4.40	Purple_Aki	Akinwale Arobieke	Akinwale Arobieke (born July 1961), known locally in North West England as Purple Aki, is a convicted criminal from Liverpool, United Kingdom. Arobieke is a 6 ft 5 in (196 cm) tall bodybuilder who weighs 20 stone (130 kg). His criminal activities are sexually motivated, a fact which was recognised in 2006 by Liverpool Magistrates' Court, when Merseyside Police successfully applied to them for a Sexual Offences Prevention Order.	
